          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Tap into your home equity\nWhen you make payments to your mortgage, you build equity in your home. Your home equity is the difference between your property's market value and the outstanding balance of your mortgage plus any other debts secured by your property. If you need funds, you can refinance your mortgage to access up to 80% of your home's appraised value 1 in cash.\nEstimate your available equity and find out how much you may qualify to borrow with our home equity calculator .",
